# Cursor Rules — Maropost Design System

## Read First
- `CLAUDE.md` — full project architecture, component APIs, conventions
- `CLAUDE_CODE_PROMPT.md` — product spec from live app observation
- `src/design-tokens/tokens.json` — all design values

## Stack
Vue 3.5 + Vuetify 3.12 + TypeScript 5.9 + Vite 7 + Pinia 3

## Component Rules

### Creating a new component
1. File: `src/components/MpComponentName.vue`
2. Use `<script setup lang="ts">`
3. Type props: `defineProps<{ title: string; count?: number }>()`
4. Type emits: `defineEmits<{ (e: 'update', val: string): void }>()`
5. Scoped styles only: `<style scoped>`
6. Write story: `MpComponentName.stories.ts` alongside the component
7. Reference design tokens — never hardcode colors/spacing

### Modifying an existing component
1. Read the component file first
2. Read its `.stories.ts` file
3. Update both component and story together
4. Run `npm run storybook` to verify

## Styling

### Do
- Use Vuetify utility classes: `d-flex`, `pa-4`, `gap-3`, `text-medium-emphasis`
- Use `v-card flat border rounded="lg"` for cards (no shadows)
- Use `MpStatusChip` for all status displays (pass correct `type` prop)
- Use design token SCSS variables: `$mp-spacing-4`, `$mp-borderRadius-md`
- Use scoped styles

### Don't
- Don't hardcode hex colors in templates or styles
- Don't use `elevation="4"` or heavy shadows
- Don't use `v-dialog` for forms (use `MpFormDrawer` instead)
- Don't use `!important` (except in rare utility overrides)
- Don't create unnamed slots
- Don't use inline styles in templates
- Don't mix icon libraries (MDI only via `mdi-*`)

## Page View Pattern

Every data page follows this layout:
```vue
<template>
  <MpPageHeader title="..." subtitle="..." :breadcrumbs="[...]">
    <template #actions>
      <v-btn color="primary" prepend-icon="mdi-plus">Create</v-btn>
    </template>
  </MpPageHeader>
  <MpFilterTabs v-model="activeTab" :tabs="[...]" />
  <v-card flat border class="mt-4">
    <MpDataTableToolbar v-model:search="search">
      <template #actions>...</template>
    </MpDataTableToolbar>
    <v-data-table :headers="headers" :items="filteredItems" />
    <MpEmptyState v-if="!filteredItems.length" ... />
  </v-card>
  <MpFloatingBulkBar :count="selected.length" @clear="selected = []">
    ...bulk actions...
  </MpFloatingBulkBar>
</template>
```

## Design Tokens
- Source: `src/design-tokens/tokens.json`
- Generated: `src/design-tokens/generated/` (don't edit these)
- Rebuild: `npm run tokens:build`

## File Naming
- Components: `PascalCase` with `Mp` prefix → `MpStatusChip.vue`
- Stories: `MpStatusChip.stories.ts` (co-located)
- Views: `PascalCase` → `SalesOrders.vue`
- Stores: `camelCase` with `use` prefix → `useCommerce.ts`
- Styles: `kebab-case` → `global.scss`

## Commit Messages
Format: `[type]: description`
Types: feat, fix, docs, refactor, perf, test, chore
Example: `[feat]: add MpDateRangePicker with story`
